#  name         movement  attack  combat  guns  hull
#  =================================================
#  Artillery    1         7       5       0     0
#  Caravel      4         0       2       0     4
#  Merchantman  5         0       6       1     8
#  Galleon      6         0       10      4     20
#  Privateer    8         8       8       4     12
#  Frigate      6         16      16      12    32
#  Man-O-War    5         24      24      32    64
